headline: Avis Budget Group (CAR) Misses Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Avis Budget (CAR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -95.05% and -0.90%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
